data.text:
Oliver Parker is a partner within the Technology team and has a focus on software and IT services. Oliver has more than 15 years of M&A experience across the technology sector and has worked on over 40 transactions for clients in the UK and across Europe.

Oliver joined Alantra from Arma Partners and prior to that, he was a member of the technology team at William Blair.
